  1→/*! @file streaming.c
  2→ * @brief Real-time data streaming engine for analog and digital samples.
  3→ *
  4→ * This module manages the data acquisition and streaming pipeline:
  5→ * 1. Deferred interrupt task: Collects samples from ADC/DIO into object pool
  6→ * 2. Streaming task: Encodes samples (CSV/JSON/ProtoBuf) and writes to outputs
  7→ *
  8→ * Key features:
  9→ * - Uses object pool (not heap) for O(1) sample allocation
 10→ * - Supports 15kHz+ sample rates with 512-sample queue depth
 11→ * - Single-interface streaming to prevent bandwidth contention
 12→ * - FPU context saving for voltage conversion in streaming task
 13→ *
 14→ * @see AInSample.c for object pool implementation
 15→ * @see csv_encoder.c for CSV output format
 16→ */
